===Format===
* '''League Stage:''''' June 13th - 15th, 2023
** 27 teams, divided equally into 3 groups of 9.
** 3 matchdays.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 18 teams}} qualify for ''Finals''.
<div style=margin-top:12px/>
* '''Finals:''''' June 16th - 17th, 2023
** 18 teams.
** 10 matches (5 matches each day).
*** Map Order: ''Erangel -> Miramar -> Erangel -> Miramar -> Erangel''

